These are Puzzles for 6x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, sprite, fanta, hot-chocolate
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, orange, watermelon, raspberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, chess, camping, sudoku
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, analyst, accountant, paramedic
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, disco, hip-hop, indie
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, golf, ice-hockey, cricket
 1. the paramedic is on the far right##1
 2. the person drinking fanta is the fan of gospel##1
 3. the fan of disco is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
 4. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person eating orange##1
 5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person eating raspberry##1
 6. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 7. the accountant is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the fan of indie##2
 8. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 9. the fan of gospel is on the right of the firefighter##1
10. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the accountant and the person eating raspberry##2
11. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
12. the paramedic is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
13. the fan of hip-hop is between the fan of disco and the person who's hobby is camping##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate        | sprite       | fanta  | milk |
| Food          | raspberry     | watermelon         | orange     | nectarine    |
| Hobby         | chess  | baking      | camping   | sudoku     |
| Job           | analyst | firefighter | accountant   | paramedic     |
| Music-Genre   | disco    | hip-hop         | gospel | indie         |
| Sport         | cricket     | lacrosse     | golf  | ice-hockey       |

