.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, lemonade, cola, juice
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, dancing, woodworking, gardening
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, sports, adventure, lemonadesy
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, ambient, techno, pop
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, indonesian, dutch, nigerian
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, scooter, van, tram
 1. the indonesian is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person driving the trike##2
 2. the nigerian is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
 3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the argentine##1
 4. the indonesian is between the person drinking tea and the person driving the van##2
 5. the fan of jazz is the person drinking lemonade##1
 6. the fan of techno is on the far right##1
 7. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
 8. the person driving the van is between the person watching scientific movies and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
 9. the person watching sports movies is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
10. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
11. the fan of jazz is the person watching adventure movies##1
12. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
13. the dutch is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
14. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | juice    | lemonade       | cola   | tea |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks     | woodworking   | gardening    | dancing  |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific    | adventure | sports   | lemonadesy     |
| Music-Genre   | pop    | jazz       | ambient | techno        |
| Nationality   | nigerian | dutch   | indonesian     | argentine    |
| Transport     | scooter       | van        | tram      | trike        |

