.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, coffee, juice, almond-milk
There 4 different types of food: cucumber, lettuce, papaya, radish
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, italian, pakistani, indian
4 different pets are kept: ferret, turtle, hedgehog, horse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, swimming, lacrosse, cycling
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, motorbike, ship, snowmobile
 1. the italian is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 4. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the indian##1
 5. the person who's sport is cycling is the person drinking juice##1
 6. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
 7. the person driving the snowmobile is between the pakistani and the person drinking almond-milk##2
 8. the person drinking coffee is the owner of the turtle##1
 9. the person drinking sprite is between the person driving the snowmobile and the owner of the ferret##2
10. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
11. the person drinking almond-milk is the person driving the ship##1
12. the person eating papaya is the person driving the motorbike##1
13. the owner of the hedgehog is between the person eating cucumber and the italian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage      | juice      | sprite        | coffee | almond-milk      |
| Food          | cucumber   | papaya       | lettuce          | radish   |
| Nationality   | canadian     | pakistani    | italian      | indian  |
| Pet           | ferret    | hedgehog     | turtle       | horse      |
| Sport         | cycling | swimming    | lacrosse        | tennis |
| Transport     | tram       | motorbike | snowmobile           | ship   |

