 8. the person driving the skateboard is the person watching thriller movies##1
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is between the writer and the person who's hobby is quad-biked-games##2
10. the dutch is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is quad-biked-games is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
12. the social-worker is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
13. the person drinking coffee is the person drinking coffee##1
14. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the pakistani##1

