.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, tea, iced-tea, water
There 4 different types of food: apple, asparagus, pepper, mango
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, lawyer, teacher, coach
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, folk, d&b, blues
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, brazilian, french, polish
4 different pets are kept: lizard, hamster, horse, fish
 1. the person eating apple is on the right of the japanese##1
